  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      After bariatric surgery there are big changes in the daily functions, activities and social
      participation of the patients.

      This is a prospective study that examine daily performance and daily participation by
      questionnaires, before and after bariatric surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
